      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Here's a wonderful opportunity to own a solid, dependable vehicle that's been genuinely well cared for! This car is in good condition inside and out \u2014 you'll find it's been maintained with everyday attention and is ready to serve you reliably for miles to come. There's normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that takes away from its appeal or performance. If you're looking for a trustworthy ride at a fair price, this one is well worth a look!",
