    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\u2728 **Stunning Mint Condition Find!** This car is truly a cut above \u2014 featuring a gleaming, blemish-free exterior, a spotless and fresh interior that looks and smells like new, and an engine that runs smoothly and confidently. Every detail has been well cared for, from the clean undercarriage to the pristine upholstery. If you're looking for a used car that feels as close to new as possible without the new-car price tag, this is your opportunity. Don't miss out on this exceptional, move-in-ready vehicle!",
      "price": 46000.0,
