      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced to reflect its current condition! This vehicle is available at an honest, no-nonsense price for buyers who are handy or looking for an affordable entry point. It shows significant wear inside and out \u2014 expect visible cosmetic imperfections, aging interior materials, and mechanical issues that will need attention. If you're a DIY enthusiast or a buyer who doesn't mind rolling up your sleeves, this could be a rewarding find at a price that leaves room in the budget for repairs. Sold as-is \u2014 what you see is what you get!",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at a price that honestly reflects its fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear including some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas, though the body structure remains solid. The interior has moderate wear on the seats and trim consistent with regular use, and the dashboard shows some scuffs. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has some age-related issues that a buyer should be aware of \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection to fully assess its mechanical state. This is a practical, usable vehicle for a buyer who understands they're getting a well-used car at a fair price, not a showroom-quality example.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with potential buyers about what to expect. The exterior has significant wear \u2014 multiple dents, deep scratches, and noticeable rust in several areas, along with faded and peeling paint. The interior shows heavy use, with worn and torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and various trim pieces that are damaged or missing. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention: it runs, but not reliably, and prospective buyers should budget for meaningful repairs. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a parts vehicle, or a project car enthusiast. No attempt has been made to hide or cosmetically mask any of the deficiencies \u2014 what you see is what you get. Priced accordingly at $6,500.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is priced to reflect that \u2014 please read carefully before inquiring. The exterior shows significant cosmetic damage, including multiple deep scratches, paint chips, dents, and fading across several panels. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and staining throughout. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs before relying on it for regular use. This is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or someone looking for parts. No warranties or guarantees are offered, and the car is sold strictly as-is. Priced accordingly for a straightforward, no-surprises transaction.",
      "price": 4500.0,
